body_html:
@tyfkda I hope the Xcode version you are using is Xcode 8 ? I was able to get everything working with Xcode 7.3 without the changes you made in this commit. However, I required to add the change you made in order to get tensor flow properly working and build the app without error in Xcode 8. The app builds fine for an iOS 10 iPhone but crashes.

Are you using using an iOS 10 device ?
I cannot make it work for iOS 10 with Xcode 8.

Could you please share your versions and all ? That would be really helpful. I can, then, maybe raise a proper question at Stack Overflow.

Thanks !
